# HW3 Problem 4: Cruise Control with PID

This implements a PID controller for cruise control in Lustre.

## Build
make -f Makefile3 cruisectr2-exe

## Simulation
make -f Makefile3 cruisectr2-sim

## PID Tuning
The PID parameters are set to example values. Tune Kgain, Ti, Td experimentally for better performance.

Compare with old controller by running simulations and observing outputs.